	<style>
	/* width */
	::-webkit-scrollbar {
		width: 10px;
	}

	/* Track */
	::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
		background: #444;
	}

	/* Handle */
	::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
		background: #888;
	}

	/* Handle on hover */
	::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
		background: #222;
	}

	body {
		background-color: #333;
	}

	.grid-container {
		background-color: #333;
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
		padding: 10px;
		row-gap: 15px;
		column-gap: 15px;
		text-align: center;
		width: 95%;
		height: 100%;
		margin: auto;
	}

	.grid-item {
		overflow: hidden;
		margin: auto;
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 20px;
		font-size: 20px;
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 321px;
		background-color: #222;
		height: 192px;
		object-fit: cover;
		transition: all 0.15s ease-in-out;
		z-index: 1;
		text-overflow: ellipsis;
		word-wrap: break-word;
	}

	.grid-item:hover {
		transform: scale(1.05);
	}

	.grid-item:hover a {
		opacity: 1;
	}

	.grid-item a {
		overflow: scroll;
		opacity: 0;
		position: absolute;
		z-index: 112;
		bottom: 0;
		left: -10px;
		margin-bottom: -45px;
		right: 0;
		color: #fff;
		font-size: 24px;
		height: 80px;
		width: calc(100% + 30px);
		background-color: #111;
		/* a */
	}

	.grid-item img {
		max-width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	/* Add a black background color to the top navigation */
	.topnav {
		background-color: #333;
		overflow: hidden;
		position: fixed;
		margin: auto;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		z-index: 30;
		width: 100%;
	}

	/* Style the links inside the navigation bar */
	.topnav a {
		float: left;
		color: #f2f2f2;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 14px 16px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 17px;
	}

	/* Change the color of links on hover */
	.topnav a:hover {
		background-color: #444;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	.topnav a {
		color: #f2f2f2;
		text-align: center;
		padding: 14px 16px;
		text-decoration: none;
		font-size: 20px;
		height: 24px;
	}

	.topnav span:hover {
		background-color: #444;
		cursor: pointer;
	}

	/* Add a color to the active/current link */
	.topnav a.active {
		background-color: #666;
		color: white;
	}

	.search {
    overflow: hidden;
		display: block;
		width: 95%;
		height: 35px;
		background-color: #444;
		padding: 10px;
		border-radius: 40px;
		position: fixed;
		left: 0;
		right: 0;
		margin: auto;
		z-index: 12;
    position: absolute;
	}

      position: absolute;
      outline: none;

      font-size: 20px;
      width: 100%;

      color: #fff;
	   	transition: all 0.2s ease-in-out;

    }

      cursor: pointer;

      color: #fff;
      font-size: 18px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .bookmarkletsButton:hover {
  		transform: scale(1.1);

  -webkit-user-select: none;

	const openGame = (url, title) => {
		const win = window.open();
    
		if(url.includes("flash/flashPlayer.html?game=")) {
			url = "https://wada.stupid1.ga/" + url;
		}
		url = encodeURIComponent(url);
    let iframe = win.document.createElement('iframe');
    iframe.src=`https://game-central.github.io/taco-unblocks-externals/index.html?name=${title}&url=${url}`;
    iframe.style.width='100%';
    iframe.style.height='100%';
    iframe.style.border='none';
    iframe.id='iframe';
    win.document.body.appendChild(iframe);

    
    let jquery = win.document.createElement('script')
    jquery.src='https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.6.1/jquery.min.js';
    win.document.head.appendChild(jquery);
    
    
    let script = win.document.createElement('script')
    script.innerHTML = `
    document.title = 'Taco Unblocks | ${title}';
    document.head.innerHTML = document.head.innerHTML + '<link rel="icon" href="data:image/png;base64,">' 
    `
    win.document.head.appendChild(script);
  
		win.document.body.style.margin = '0px';
		win.document.body.style.height = '100vh';
		win.document.body.style.backgroundColor = '#333';
	};
    
    
    
	const search = () => {
		const text = document.querySelector("#search").value.toLowerCase();
		const items = [...document.querySelectorAll(".grid-item a")];
		items.forEach(i => {
			if(i.innerHTML.toLowerCase().includes(text)) {
				i.parentElement.style.display = "block";
			} else {
				i.parentElement.style.display = "none";
			}
		});
	}
  
  //No More Ctrl + U (View Source)
  $(document).ready(function(){
  ctrl = false;
  document.addEventListener("keydown", function(e){
    if(e.which == 17){
      ctrl = true;
    }
    if(e.which == 85 && ctrl == true){
      e.preventDefault();
    
    }
  }, true);

  document.addEventListener("keyup", function(e){
    if(e.which == 17){
      ctrl = false;

    }
  });
});
